{"about_the_game":"ZombCube is a first-person, cross-platform, zombie survival, wave based game. Play solo or with friends all over the world destroying the evil ZombCube's. Use teamwork, leadership, and skills to be the best and rank on the leaderboards.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nZombCube was designed to allow students to follow along and incorporate a lot of cross-platform features. We look into Unity Ads, In-App Purchases, Unity's New Input System, Pathfinding, and networking.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nControls:<br />\r\nMove: WASD/Left Stick<br />\r\nLook: Mouse/Right Stick<br />\r\nJump: Space/Bottom Button<br />\r\nFire: LMB/Right trigger<br />\r\nSwap Weapons: Q/Top Button<br />\r\nWeapon Select: Hold Q/Top Button<br />\r\nQuick Switch: 1,2,3,4/D-Pad<br />\r\nInteract: Hold E/Button Left<br />\r\nPause: Esc/P/Start Button<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\nMultiplayer<br />\r\nSingleplayer<br />\r\nBlasters<br />\r\nSkins<br />\r\nMusic<br />\r\nLeaderboards<br />\r\nAchievements<br />\r\nSci-Fi Texture Pack<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBlaster Model &amp; Animations:<br />\r\nDakota Hamilton<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGrenade Model &amp; Projectile Particle VFX:<br />\r\nJacob Price<br />\r\n<br />\r\nZombie Voice Actor:<br />\r\nRiley Hutton<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayer Voice Actors:<br />\r\nJakob Dylan Cook<br />\r\nMorgan Houston<br />\r\nLydia Jackson<br />\r\nAshton Null<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMusic:<br />\r\nblackSnow by airtone<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSci-Fi Texture Pack 1:<br />\r\nFireBolt Studios (Unity Asset Store)","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Stayin' Alive Alone","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3035180/4115ac71a7e1f1c07d5cf7b9ccb8571e1fdaab25.jpg"},{"name":"Stayin' Alive Together","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3035180/4115ac71a7e1f1c07d5cf7b9ccb8571e1fdaab25.jpg"},{"name":"Cube Destroyer I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3035180/4115ac71a